0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"04afb493900e938fbf4cc06a3fbed6c038a4b9b0","tid":853640,"uid":137479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T18:14:34.000Z","msg":"想啊 但係你點喚醒其他人願意咁做<br />\n我想改變<br />\n但係我地生活緊係呢個世界 已經被逼維持緊呢個醜惡嘅現實 革命囉無計㗎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T18:29:47.000Z","msg":"有改變既想法但係又冇能力，<br />\n有能力既人又冇改變既想法。<br />\n<br />\n真係好無言<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13cd65db30d2ed5635c6224fda0e43550990f814","tid":853640,"uid":207470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T18:35:48.000Z","msg":"咁你想點改變？"},{"pid":"afb20f24393122f359624f788a25444588deaea8","tid":853640,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T18:38:46.000Z","msg":"我覺得一旦會咁樣諗既人，就已經番唔到轉頭，因為係佢哋眼中，所有野都係為左自己"},{"pid":"ae88007667f3c1e9ad4deb29f0522b31ba3860e4","tid":853640,"uid":208252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13cd65db30d2ed5635c6224fda0e43550990f814","tid":853640,"uid":207470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T18:35:48.000Z","msg":"咁你想點改變？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T18:43:45.000Z","msg":"我無辦法改變哂所有人既思想，<br />\n但我想用我既講話去感染我接觸到既人，<br />\n可以同生命抱有尊重而已<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪好白痴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eec5607d9ede9a2120b6da62ab5e5bc6b862ec8","tid":853640,"uid":207470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae88007667f3c1e9ad4deb29f0522b31ba3860e4","tid":853640,"uid":208252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13cd65db30d2ed5635c6224fda0e43550990f814","tid":853640,"uid":207470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T18:35:48.000Z","msg":"咁你想點改變？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T18:43:45.000Z","msg":"我無辦法改變哂所有人既思想，<br />\n但我想用我既講話去感染我接觸到既人，<br />\n可以同生命抱有尊重而已<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪好白痴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T18:48:3